						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 7 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold <hi rend="italic">(tuḷaippoṉ)</hi> for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Tirumūlaṭṭānattu-Perumānaḍigaḷ at Tirunalakkuṉṟam in Kuṉṟiyūrnāḍu by <hi rend="bold">Vaḷavaṉ Pēraraiyaṉ a resident of Nirppaḻaṉi</hi> in Uṟattūr-kūṟṟam. This might be assigned to <hi rend="bold">Parāntaka I.</hi> (No. 68, <hi rend="italic">Pud. Ins.</hi> Texts).</p>						

						</summary>
